Query: When I click on the Home About or Contact links in the header, the highlighting remains even after I move the mouse away. How can I fix this? The same issue also occurs for the same links in the mobile menu. I want the highlighting to only appear when the mouse is over the link, and to disappear when the mouse moves away.

