      if (e.key === 'Escape' && mobileMenu.classList.contains('active')) {
        closeMobileMenu();
      }
    });
    ```
- **ARIA attributes:** `aria-haspopup`, `aria-expanded`, `aria-label` and `role="menu"` on dropdowns.

